Subject: Database Report Error
Description: After adding a new SQL database to the scan, the customer noticed "No data available" in the Report.
DevOps_Steps_to_Reproduce__c:
Launch NEA
Navigate to the Database node under the job folder
SQL folder > Permission folder
A new folder is created for the custom report
Some reports show the data, and some have missing data.
What_We_Know__c:
We noticed some mission data from some databases.
The DBA thinks the issue is that NEA does not consistently write the data to the table.
Since the customer is not on the latest version and we have released some patches related to database performance, I advise the customer to upgrade.
Next_Steps__c: I will decide after the customer upgrades to the latest version.
Solution_Comment__c: The customer will take the issue to his internal team
Account_Name__c: Woodmen of the World Life Insurance Society
